description: Cactus Corn has provided the people of Phoenix with their sweet & salty fix since 1998 with its amazingly tasty gourmet selection of Arizona Kettle Corn. This cool truck is run by the ever-friendly Levandowski family who has mastered the art of popping Cactus Corn to perfection. You can tell when you taste every delightfully fluffy and crunchy kernel. You’ll also find refreshing frozen lemonade and shaved ice with all your favorite flavors. These delicious carnival treats are perfect for any occasion so next time you’re planning an exciting event, have Cactus Corn pop on by and supply some wonderfully flavorful fun!
name: Cactus Corn
